; Coverage for report.cc fn_lot_price
; Tests the lot_price function which returns the price annotation from a lot
; Uses lot with price annotation to exercise the details.price branch

2024/03/15 * Buy Stock
    Assets:Brokerage          10 AAPL {$150.00}
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(lot_price(amount))\n" Assets:Brokerage
$150
end test
